<li class='cover' id='bookCover_44890073'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/44890073-all-the-ways-we-said-goodbye"><img alt="All the Ways We Said Goodbye" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1566234003l/44890073._SX98_.jpg" />
